file.name: k8s-resource-apis.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.2"
info:
  title: version api
  version: "1.0"
paths:
  /orchestrator/k8s/resource/inception/info:
    get:
      responses:
        "200":
          description: this api give you inception pod info, such as pod name
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  code:
                    type: integer
                    description: status code
                  status:
                    type: string
                    description: status
                  result:
                    type: object
                    description: string
                    $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResourceInfo'

components:
  schemas:
    ResourceInfo:
      type: object
      required:
        - podName
      properties:
        podName:
          type: string
          description: pod name
